     Azure_Cache_for_Redis:::dataStoreService
     Azure_Monitor:::azureService
     Azure_AD:::azureService
     Azure_Key_Vault:::azureService
     Azure_Logic_Apps_Scheduler:::azureService
     External_APIs:::external
     User:::external
     Admin:::external
